---
// Who We Are - Visual Timeline Layout
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
        Our Journey in Water Innovation
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-foreground/80">
        From vision to global impact
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Challenge -->
    <div class="mt-24 bg-primary/5 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">The Water Crisis Today</h3>
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-6">
          While 90% of climate adaptation needs are water-based, less than 5% of climate finance is directed toward water solutions. 
          This critical gap is where we focus our efforts.
        </p>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto my-8"></div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Our Vision for the Future</h4>
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-8">
          We envision a world where water security drives peace, stability, and prosperity for all. 
          Through innovation, investment, and collaboration, we're making this vision a reality.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
          Join Our Mission
          <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
